Annotation Type IncrementCounterInCache


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value=METHOD)
public @interface IncrementCounterInCache
    Increments by 1 single counter under given key. If counter doesn't exist it will be initialized with value 1.

    Author:

    • Element Detail

      • namespace

        public abstract String namespace
        A namespace that is added to the key as it is stored in the distributed cache. This allows differing object that may have the same ID to coexist. This value must be assigned.
        Returns:
        the namespace for the objects cached in the given method.
        Default:
        "[unassigned]"
